{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reduce overseas aid spending to \u00a31 billion",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The Government currently spends nearly over \u00a313 billion per year on overseas aid. \r\n\r\nWe believe this is madness and that it is time to focus our priorities at home. We call on the Government to reduce the overseas aid budget to \u00a31 billion and spend our money at home.",
